<BaseLayout title="Prompt Iteration Workflow" description="A simple workflow for testing and improving AI image prompts." canonicalPath="/guides/prompt-iteration-workflow/"><article class="content-section article-body"><h1>Prompt Iteration Workflow</h1><p>Save a baseline prompt, then change one major group at a time: pose, camera, lighting, or style. Compare results before making the next change.</p><p>The Prompt Cart helps you keep useful fragments separate. If the final prompt grows past the point of readability, remove weaker fragments and regenerate from the cart.</p></article></BaseLayout>
